OL,6,FHarrods' current owners said they are
OL,7,F"utterly appalled" by the allegations
OL,8,Fof abuse perpetrated by the late
OL,9,Fbillionaire.
OL,11,FThey said: "As a business we failed
OL,12,Four employees who were his victims and
OL,13,Ffor this we sincerely apologise."
